        <p>Tools in the Standard toolbar let you perform basic functions, such as Save, Cut, Copy, Paste, Undo, and Redo. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare,Products.Analyzer">There are also shortcut buttons for performing source control functions, as well as sending documents to other applications (e.g., opening a topic's true code in Notepad in order to edit the tags). </MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.MovieSync">There are also shortcuts buttons for opening the Frames window pane and Properties window pane. </MadCap:conditionalText>To see this toolbar you can select <span class="Emphasis">View&gt;Toolbars&gt;Standard</span>.</p>
